{
  "stem": "18575.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 45.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Supposedly IG Farben industry is the one that, what I learned later, induced the SS to build Auschwitz for the production of military supplies such as powders, and weapons, and synthetic rubber, and synthetic oil.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were also coal mines, because that was all inside Silesia, which was the coal mine district [INAUDIBLE] in Poland, also attached to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there were many camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The camp, my camp, that-- where they sent me to Buna was called Auschwitz II.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we-- yes, when we arrived at Auschwitz again, we had to undress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went through a selecktia, they call it-- selection-- where the SS officer, whoever he was, looked at you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to run past him and back again naked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, either you went-- he made a move to the right or to the left on a field, which, one means you were accepted, and the other, you went for recuperation, as they state in their book, which was the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I passed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, he looked at me at my buttock, this-- the thing I had it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, what's that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, and I said-- I lied, and I said-- oh, I had it many, many years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he just let me go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We then were set up in a single row-- there were a few hundreds of us-- and given pieces of paper with a number on it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And prisoners came with the tattoo needles and tattooed the number.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The number that I-- that was tattooed on me is 127956, or in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my name, my address, my identity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this, on the left forearm--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- it was my total identity.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
